posts.post_title: Help me finish my T205 Set!
posts.post_content:
I'm down to my last five cards in a low-grade T205 set. Please let me know if you have any of the following you'd be willing to sell:

Bresnahan (Mouth open)
Dougherty (White sock)
Krause
A.P. Leifield
Pfiester

I also have an extra T205 Turner I'd be willing to trade, depending on the return. One is in poor condition, the other is a nice looking SGC 30.

I may have a few of those available depending on the grade you're looking for.  PM me your address and I'll send you a list of what I have.

Thanks!
